summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to certain property ("Blue Streak" Park and Ride Lot) - in the north half of the southeast quarter of the northeast quarter of the southeast quarter of Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, authorizing the purchase thereof by funds heretofore appropriated for such purpose by Ordinance 101360 and funds to be received by the City pursuant to an Urban Mass Transportation Capital Grant Contract with the United States of America (Project No. WA-03-0013, Contract No. DOT-UT-899).
